         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">22 June 1866. ¶  ¶ I have the honor to request that for the future all requisitions on the Public Works Department may be forwarded quarterly and prior to the last day in each quarter. ¶  ¶ I am to in...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">66.06.22a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From John Moore</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">E2371, unit 10, p. 161, VPRS 1187/P outward correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Trans 19.3.91. To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to J. Moore, 22 June 1866.</p>
               </note>22 June 1866.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to request that for the future all requisitions on the Public Works Department may be forwarded quarterly and prior to the last day in each quarter.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am to inform you that all such requisitions which may be received subsequent thereto will be considered as not requiring to be dealt with until those of the succeeding quarter are received</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am further to point out that under this Rule requisitions received after the 29th of September cannot be given effect to until the votes of the following year are available</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This rule is not however intended to apply to works of great urgency but to ordinary cases only.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">(Sd) J. Moore</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director Botanic Gardens</p>
         </div>
      </body>
